<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2600979>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Holotype of Leptobrachella shangsiensis sp. nov. (NHMG1704002): (A) Dorsal view, (B) dorsolateral view, (C) flank and lateral view, (D) ventral view, (E) volar view of the left hand, and (F) thenar view of the left foot." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2600979/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2600983>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Leptobrachella shangsiensis sp. nov. in habitat (Photo taken in situ)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2600983/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2600985>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. The advertisement call of holotype of Leptobrachella shangsiensis sp. nov. Expanded about 2 s waveform with Oscillogram (top) and corresponding audiospectrogram (bottom). The ambient air temperature was 21.5°C." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2600985/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2600987>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. (A) Breeding habitat of Leptobrachella shangsiensis sp. nov. and (B) deforestation in Shiwandashan National Nature Reserve, Guangxi Province, China." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2600987/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

